! This branch hosts the developing version

-------------------------------------------

Instructions to compile the fortran subroutines:

With ifort:

f2py -c -m pyn_fort_general pyn_fort_general.f90
f2py -c -m pyn_fort_gnm pyn_fort_gnm.f90 -lmkl_intel_lp64 -lmkl_sequential -lmkl_core -lmkl_def -lpthread

With gfortran in Goldrake:

f2py2 -c -m pyn_fort_general pyn_fort_general.f90
f2py2 -c -m pyn_fort_gnm pyn_fort_gnm.f90 -llapack